## Limitations

The findings presented in this report are based on available online resources and may not encompass the full spectrum of scientific research on nostalgia. Additionally, the subjective nature of nostalgia means that individual experiences can vary widely, and the conclusions drawn here may not apply universally. Further empirical research is needed to explore the nuances of nostalgia and its impact on different populations.